119
00:10:38,282 --> 00:10:46,869
[SPEAKER_02]: Well, trying to help with, you know, the overall budget for the city, but I believe we'll be able to keep up with the cyclicals and not fall behind with those 8 hours.

120
00:10:47,389 --> 00:10:47,650
[SPEAKER_02]: Okay.

121
