[SPEAKER_07]: All right.

147
00:11:45,604 --> 00:11:49,986
[SPEAKER_07]: Seeing no further questions on the assessing department, we'll move to facilities.

148
00:11:51,047 --> 00:11:53,188
[SPEAKER_07]: And we have our new facilities director here with us.

149
